page.title: 11A day in my life
page.content:
****************
Hello, my name is Laura. I am twelve years old. On school days I wake up at 7:30am. On week-ends I wake up about 9:30am. After I wake up I get washed and dressed then have my breakfast. I catch the bus to school each week, Monday to Friday. I catch the bus at about 8:30am. We get to school at about 8:45am. I live three miles from my school. When school starts at 9:00am we have tutor time for twenty minutes before going to our next lesson. Usually on Monday it would be Technical Drawing. We have play time at 10:30am and then at 12:05pm we have lunch. My favorite part of te weekday is home time at 4:00pm. School finishes at 3:30pm but by th time I get home it is 4:00pm. I go to bed at about 10:30pm.
